Description: BW Offshore Limited is a Bermuda-based holding company that owns and operates oil and gas floating, production, storage and offloading vessels (FPSOs). The Companys activities are construction, lease and operation of FPSOs as well as offshore floating wind. The Company has a fleet of approximately 10 FPSOs, operating in Africa, Europe, Southeast Asia & Oceania, and Americas. The Company owned fleet included the vessels, such as Abo FPSO, BW Adolo, Espoir Ivoirien, Petroleo Nautipa, Sendje Berge, BW Athena, BW Catcher, BW Cidade de Sao Vicente, BW Pioneer, FPSO Polvo, YUUM KAKNAAB, BW Joko Tole, BW Opportunity and Umuroa. The Companys subsidiaries include Berge Carmen Singapore Pte Ltd, Bergesen Worldwide Offshore Mexico S. de RL de CV, BW Abo Pte Ltd, BW Athena Pte Ltd, BW Berge Helene Pte Ltd, BW Offshore (UK) Limited, Prosafe Production B.V., Tinworth Pte Ltd, Tinworth France SAS, BW Offshore SPV B.V, BW Offshore Shipholding Pte Ltd, BW Adolo Pte Ltd and BW Offshore EPC FZE.
